---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section class="books-container">
        <h1>My Bookshelf</h1>
        <p>Here are some books I've enjoyed reading:</p>
        
        <ul class="book-list">
            <li>
                <strong>The Pragmatic Programmer</strong> by Andrew Hunt & David Thomas
                <p>A classic guide to software craftsmanship that has influenced developers for generations.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Atomic Habits <a href="/books/atomic-habits" class="notes-link">Notes</a></strong> by James Clear
                
                <!-- <div class="book-title">
                    <a href="/books/atomic-habits" class="notes-link">Notes</a>
                </div> -->
                <p>An easy and proven way to build good habits and break bad ones.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Dune</strong> by Frank Herbert
                <p>A masterpiece of science fiction that explores politics, religion, and ecology.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Sapiens: A Brief History of Humankind</strong> by Yuval Noah Harari
                <p>A thought-provoking exploration of the history of our species.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>The Design of Everyday Things</strong> by Don Norman
                <p>A manifesto for human-centered design that changed how we think about usability.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .books-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .book-list {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .book-list li {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .book-list strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        color: #0066cc;
    }

    .book-list p {
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
        color: #555;
    }

    /* .book-title {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    } */

    .book-title strong {
        display: inline;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .notes-link {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
        background-color: #0066cc;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
        position: relative;
        top: -1px;
    }

    .notes-link:hover {
        background-color: #0055aa;
    }
</style>